{
  "stem": "4830.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When his father came in, and he told me that he wishes me all the best, but-- but not here, because it was dangerous to harbor Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said I must leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my friend was very upset.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, at age 15, he was as tall as his father, and they almost got into a fight.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said that if I have to leave, he's going to leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So his-- his father told him that if he wants to do that, he doesn't need to come back, either.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we both left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't want him to leave, but he said that he wants to leave with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not just as a demonstration, but he managed to get into the factory where they worked, and we slept in the factory, which was fairly safe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in spite of his conviction, he was a reasonably good friend when I needed him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were a few like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not too many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say that approximately 95% percent of the Hungarian were either too afraid or were in favor of what was happening, and I would estimate those who were brave enough to take the risk to have-- not more than 5%.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Going back a bit, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] say in the '30s, what-- what do you remember about the relationships between Jews and non-Jews in that pre-war period?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a-- a relationship of continuously increasing deterioration.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we did not get extremely upset about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the accepted way of life that the Jews and Gentiles not always found understanding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were, of course, even in the early '30s-- because I can recall events as early as in 1934, '35, because I read the papers and everything that was related to politics early.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
